，ChatGPT 偏任务型的多轮对话或问答系统，定位于「通用型 AI 技术助理」。相比苹果 Siri 和小爱同学的「订餐、订票、订宾馆」，ChatGPT 更多执行开放域任务，即问答、阅读理解、推理、头脑风暴、写作文、改错等，可以说是「AI 版的知乎」。 ChatGPT 会取代搜索引擎吗？｜钛媒体深度"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-f0a7b3220fde19b2131f4c9fe37093f3_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "69 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/571427371"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I3drE1qCsqt0UEAMaCDg5MjY2MTgwIIjvy5wGMAA4wQFAIXIJNTcxNDI3MzcxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "34_1676444906.5221136", "card_id": "Q_583771329", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "对你影响最大的爱情电影是哪部？带给了你哪些触动？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-2d5c1b62a63b15c9e636e55da06a29ac_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "68 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/583771329"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I3drE1qCsqt0UEAMaCDkyMDA4ODAwIJDMp58GMAI4J0Aicgk1ODM3NzEzMjl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1676444906.5226803", "card_id": "Q_567849756", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 12}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "国内有哪些适合情侣一起旅行的浪漫景点推荐？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-fc6da6974fc85614a201fece90b0480d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "63 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_